snippet.title: Beers and Boomerangs - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOVEMBER 22nd!
A Chaotic Survival/Cooking VR game where kangaroos are stealing your beer! Multi-task between cooking for your mates and assaulting Australian fauna.

Steam - https://beersandboomerangs.com/steam
Oculus - https://www.oculus.com/experiences/quest/3767842406602776/
Oculus Demo  - https://beersandboomerangs.com/oculus
